    <h2>How to Use</h2>
    <h4>Instructions</h4>
    <ol style="padding-left: 15px;">
      <li>Open the application in your web browser by visiting the URL where it is hosted.</li>
      <li>On the home page, you will see an input field where you can paste a YouTube link.</li>
      <li>Copy a YouTube link from the YouTube website or app, and paste it into the input field.</li>
      <li>Click the "Convert" button to initiate the conversion process.</li>
      <li>The application will make a request to the Backend server to fetch the video and convert it to an MP3 file.</li>
      <li>Please allow a few moments for conversion process to complete, as this may vary depending on your internet speed. We appreciate your understanding</li>
      <li>Once the conversion process is complete, you will be prompted to download the MP3 file.</li>
      <li>Click the download button to save the file to your computer.</li>
      <li>You can also view a small iframe of the video on the page, along with its title.</li>
      <li style="margin-left: 7px;">To learn more about the application or its developer, you can visit the " About" and "Docs" pages using the links in the navigation menu.</li>
    </ol>
